About Figlet FontsThe Figlet Tool in Email Effects allows attractive text to be created with Figlet fonts. The Figlet font system was developed by Frank Sheeran, Ian Chai, Glenn Chappell (FIG) and John Cowan and is the standard system for ASCII Art fonts.Any Figlet font (whose file name ends in .flf) in the Figlet Fonts folder will be accessible from the Figlet Tool. Email Effects comes with a small selection of these Ð more can be downloaded from the Figlet page at http://st-www.cs.uiuc.edu/~chai/figlet.html. There is also more information about the Figlet font system at that site.Sig Softwarehttp://www.sigsoftware.com/